# HosLaw  Ontario Legal AI Assistant

HosLaw is an AI powered legal assistant that answers questions about Ontario law using natural language processing and large language models.

## Features
- Ask legal questions 
- FastAPI backend with REST endpoints
- Groq-powered LLM responses
- Clean Next.js frontend
- Designed for integration with CanLII API (in progress)

## 🧠 Tech Stack
- Python (FastAPI)
- Next.js (React)
- Groq API (LLM)
- REST API architecture

